    • getDataByPersonId

      public java.lang.String getDataByPersonId​(java.lang.Integer objectType, java.lang.Integer personId, java.lang.Integer dataLength)

      This function get datas of referee/assessor from referee/assessor ArrayList by personId.

      User can choose short or long version of data. Short: personID, GivenName, FamilyName Long: personID, GivenName, FamilyName, Nation, YOB (only referee), licence
      Parameters:
      objectType - 1: Referee, 3: Assessor
      personId - RefereeId or AssessorId
      dataLength - 1: short, 2: long
      Returns:
      short: [personId] givenName FamilyName long: [personId] givenName FamilyName Nation /YOB/ licence
